<paragraph id="4E4A7050C7EB94A63BCEF584E4310493" pageId="2" pageNumber="55">
<taxonomicName id="D8B9531B91C76FB62381C6CB8D8BA397" authority="P.Beauv." authorityName="Lange" authorityYear="1871" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Schedonorus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Schedonorus benekenii" order="Poales" pageId="2" pageNumber="55" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="benekenii">Schedonorus benekenii</taxonomicName>
Lange, Flora Danica 48: 5, t. 2826. (1871). Type Protologue: &quot;In silvia hinc inde. Specimen depictum fig. 1 in insula Lolland legit cl. E. 
<taxonomicName id="4E5C1610F037258CC9FB608A4858D3A6" family="Poaceae" genus="Rostrup" higherTaxonomySource="treatment-meta" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rostrup" order="Poales" pageId="2" pageNumber="55" rank="genus">Rostrup</taxonomicName>
, specimen fig. 2 in silva Jonstrup Vang legit cl. H. Mortensen&quot;. Type: [Denmark] Jonstrup Vang. 29TH June 1866, H. Mortensen (lectotype, designated here: C [C10021729 image!]). (Figure 3)
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
